sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant StudioShell
    participant BrowserSyncClient
    participant Tractor as Tractor (ws://localhost:42000)
    participant OPFS

    Browser->>StudioShell: load apps/me (PWA boot)
    StudioShell->>StudioShell: mount HeraldPlugin slot
    StudioShell->>StudioShell: mount FireflyPlugin slot
    StudioShell->>BrowserSyncClient: connect(ws://localhost:42000)
    BrowserSyncClient->>Tractor: WebSocket handshake
    Tractor-->>BrowserSyncClient: initial snapshot (Loro state vector)
    BrowserSyncClient-->>OPFS: persist snapshot

    Note over StudioShell,OPFS: Gate 3a complete — primitives verified

    StudioShell->>OPFS: installPlugin(url, sha256)
    OPFS-->>StudioShell: verify SHA-256 ✓ / reject ✗
    StudioShell->>StudioShell: plugin loaded in DOM slot

    Note over Browser,OPFS: Gate 3b — consolidated distro active

    Browser->>StudioShell: user writes data (offline)
    StudioShell->>OPFS: persist mutation (Loro delta)
    StudioShell->>BrowserSyncClient: queue delta

    Note over BrowserSyncClient,Tractor: tractor disconnected — offline mode

    BrowserSyncClient->>Tractor: reconnect
    BrowserSyncClient->>Tractor: replay delta (Loro sync)
    Tractor-->>BrowserSyncClient: ack + merge
